social_posts.post_text:
Join us this Friday 9/22 @9 pm, in  celebrating the return of Artscape with the official album release/listening party for OMNI, the latest album by BALTIMORES OWN @mrvershawn . 

Mister Vershawn is a rising star in the world of electronic music and DJing, with a passion for creating electrifying beats and groovy soundscapes. 

Mister Vershawn has quickly made a name for himself as a producer to watch. Drawing inspiration from a wide range of musical genres and styles, Mister Vershawn's music is a unique fusion of electronic, R&B, and Afrobeats that is guaranteed to get you moving. 

Whether behind the decks at a packed club or in the studio crafting his latest masterpiece, Mister Vershawn's energy and creativity shines through in everything he does. 

Keep an eye on this talented artist, as his music is sure to take the world by storm. 

His second album Omni that is currently available on all streaming platforms.  Link in bio for tickets.
